snippet.title: Skull Fang  (Arcade) Playthrough longplay video game
snippet.description: Skull Fang is a 1996 vertical-scrolling shooter developed and published in arcades by Data East. Skull Fang is the third and final entry in a loose trilogy of games beginning with 1989's Vapor Trail. It was released for the Sega Saturn in 1997.
